		<node ID="ID_9227201" LINK="http://www.cleveralgorithms.com/nature-inspired/stochastic/variable_neighborhood_search.html" TEXT="Variable Neighborhood Search - Clever Algorithms: Nature ">
			<node ID="ID_602884036" TEXT="Variable Neighborhood Descent (VND) refers to the use of a Local Search procedure and the deterministic (as opposed to stochastic or probabilistic) change of neighborhood size. Reduced Variable Neighborhood Search (RVNS) involves performing a stochastic random search within a neighborhood and no refinement via a local search technique." />
