			<node ID="ID_900326241" TEXT="Tabu search created by Fred W. Glover in 1986 and formalized in 1989 is a metaheuristic search method employing local search methods used for mathematical optimization.. Local (neighborhood) searches take a potential solution to a problem and check its immediate neighbors (that is solutions that are similar except for very few minor details) in the hope of finding an improved solution." />
