			<node ID="ID_917993584" TEXT="Natural Language Processing or NLP for short is broadly defined as the automatic manipulation of natural language like speech and text by software. The study of natural language processing has been around for more than 50 years and grew out of the field of linguistics with the rise of computers.[1]" />
