			</node>
		<node ID="ID_866834126" LINK="https://www.udemy.com/natural-language-processing/" TEXT="Introduction to Natural Language Processing (NLP) | Udemy">
			<node ID="ID_738237226" TEXT="This course introduces Natural Language Processing through the use of python and the Natural Language Tool Kit. Through a practical approach youll get hands on experience working with and analyzing text. As a student of this course youll get updates for free which include lecture revisions new code examples and new data projects." />
